These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: reggae, soul
1. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | soul |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, blend
1. the blend-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |
| Cigar   | tiparillo | blend |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-3::.
2 different games are played: backgammon, chess
1. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2   |
| Game   | chess | backgammon |

 #################################

 
